flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B["Define image list<br/>(img1, img2, img3)"]
    B --> C["Define filter list<br/>(grayscale, blur, sepia)"]
    C --> D{More images?}
    D -->|No| Z([End])
    D -->|Yes| E[Select next image]
    E --> F{More filters?}
    F -->|No| D
    F -->|Yes| G[Select next filter]
    G --> H["Apply filter<br/>to image"]
    H --> I["Write result<br/>to output/"]
    I --> F